{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297", "id": 22148786, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyMjE0ODc4Ng==", "number": 10297, "title": "fs::stat() returns truncated created, modified, and accessed times", "user": {"login": "williamw520", "id": 678912, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY3ODkxMg==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/678912?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520", "html_url": "https://github.com/williamw520", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/williamw520/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2013-11-05T20:31:17Z", "updated_at": "2013-11-10T21:31:14Z", "closed_at": "2013-11-10T21:31:14Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "In 0.9-pre codeline, fs::stat() returns truncated times.\n\nThe problem seems to be in uvio::fs_mkstat().  fs::stat() calls io::fs_lstat() which calls uvio::fs_mkstat().  Its to_msec() converts an C time from uv_timespec_t into Rust time.\n\n``` rust\nstruct uv_timespec_t {\n    tv_sec: libc::c_long,\n    tv_nsec: libc::c_long\n}\n```\n\ntv_sec and tv_nsec are in c_long, which can be 32-bit.  to_msec() multiplies tv_sec with 1000, which will truncate the high bits of a large 32-bit time value.  tv_sec needs to be casted to u64 before multiplied with 1000 to avoid the truncation problem.\n", "closed_by": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10297/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}